timeline.answer: The getlinked tech hackathon 1.0 is formally announced to the general public and teams begin to get ready to register
Interested teams can now show their interest in the getlinked tech hackathon 1.0 2023 by proceeding to register
Interested Participants are no longer Allowed to register

timeline.header: Announcement of the accepted teams and ideas
timeline.answer: All teams whom idea has been accepted into getlinked tech hackathon 1.0 2023 are formally announced
Accepted teams can now proceed to build their ground breaking skill driven solutions
Teams get the opportunity to pitch their projects to judges. The winner of the hackathon will also be announced on this day
